snippet.textDisplay: This is one of the most beautiful songs that I have ever heard in my life and these thankless bitches out here are hitting the dislike button. The first episode was a disaster; I agree, but get over it bitches, already! Coke Studio is taking off - I do agree that the season 9 was their biggest hit but come down to reality and face it that this one isn't going bad either. I loved this song and Jaffer's voice is like he's singing a lullaby. You can listen to this song over and over again. And for all those who have disliked the song, they have probably never said goodbyes to their loved ones, I guess. it's painful, for starters. Don't even get me started on this.
